    "text": "We always try to facilitate that innovation of our customers, to be up to date, to be able to offer our customers what they need according to what the market demands. But we have always found a very, very proactive collaborator in Holded.",
    "speaker": "José Vega",
    "role": "Co-CEO & Co-founder, FIN2GO",
